  <!-- Security & Operational Guidance -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Operational Security (OpSec)</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm text-gray-400">
      <p>
        Running autonomous agents like OpenClaw requires discipline.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Least Privilege</strong>: Generate separate Agent Tokens for different bots. Revoke if compromised.</li>
        <li><strong>Log Redaction</strong>: Ensure your agent logs do not leak PII or API tokens.</li>
        <li><strong>Sandboxing</strong>: Run your OpenClaw gateway in a containerized environment (Docker/Podman).</li>
        <li><strong>Extension Review</strong>: Only install OpenClaw skills/extensions from trusted sources.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
